g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你仲係唔明, 果然文學既野我真係識條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea0aa24fc61e57a5629930e33e3ecd65946e3ea","tid":474870,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無知到以為MF只有一個解釋 仲話自己玩左好耐120<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n繼續撐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好 連登冇得edit post, 你咪話自己玩左咁耐120都唔知mf可解做中幅嘅，而家連圖都cap埋 Medium format又係叫MF喎. 你諗左去manual focus 而諗唔到 medium format 只証明你無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e020349001533b9bb7f307546a040135809e6ebf","tid":474870,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/225946_044184cb68795749497c4db23862a54e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F225946_044184cb68795749497c4db23862a54e.jpg&h=30ec50bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講菲林 你地班on9就諗左去對焦 呢道連一個正常用家都冇 唔怪之得含撚貓都抛到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_format\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFilm_format&d=jz7IyT5goD3klYjNX%2FBXRgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f39535c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_format</a><br />\n<br />\n大家講format 丫嘛, 一齊講啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我google 35mm and MF 第一個出係manual focus 第二個已經係medium format, 外國好多人用MF係講中幅 係你地唔去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己都識講, Google 係出Manual focus 同 Medium Format, <br />\n呢個就係我叫你自己search 下既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/no